################################  The VTONF installation procedures ##############################

Requirements:
1)Server Requirements:
        a) The server must be a 32-bit  GNU/Linux server having operating system Centos 4.5 or higher.
        b) The server  must be an OpenVZ server, http://openvz.org/
	c) A hard disk partition mounted on /vz
        
2)Client Requirements:
	a) You may need Mozilla firefox web browser 1.5 or higher.

Upgrade VTONF:

To upgrade the vtonf use the following command 

	# ./upgrade

For a new installation please read the following.

Installation :

	i) Download the latest installer  of tar file vtonfinstaller.X.X.X.tar.gz , where X.X.X is the version
    	ii) Decompress the tar file
		# tar -xvzf vtonfinstaller.X.X.X.tar.gz
	iii) Change the directory
		# cd vtonfinstaller.X.X.X/
	iv) Now execure it as follows 
		# ./install

DOCUMENTATION:

        http://www.wiki.vtonf.com/

